    <title>PTES（渗透测试技术指南:诸葛建伟翻译）</title>
    <link href="http://a6361117.github.io/2017/04/13/PTES%EF%BC%88%E6%B8%97%E9%80%8F%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>http://a6361117.github.io/2017/04/13/PTES（渗透测试技术指南）/</id>
    <published>2017-04-13T05:09:51.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-03-10T08:13:34.631Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>找到了一个关于渗透测试指南的脑图，就找了下有没有中文的，还真给我找到了，就顺便整理成了TXT的格式放到了博客上给大家看。<br>PTES(渗透测试技术指南)<br>1前期交互阶段<br>2情报搜集<br>3威胁建模<br>4漏洞分析<br>5渗透攻击<br>6后渗透攻击<br>7报告<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="一、前期交互阶段"><a href="#一、前期交互阶段" class="headerlink" title="一、前期交互阶段"></a>一、前期交互阶段</h2><h3 id="1-确定范围"><a href="#1-确定范围" class="headerlink" title="1.确定范围"></a>1.确定范围</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1）如何确定范围</span><br><span class="line">2）时间估计</span><br><span class="line">I.预估整体项目的时间周期</span><br><span class="line">II.确定以小时计的额外技术支持</span><br><span class="line">3）问答交谈</span><br><span class="line">I.对业务管理部门的问答交流</span><br><span class="line">II.对系统管理员的问答交流</span><br><span class="line">III.对IT支持的问答交流</span><br><span class="line">IV.与普通雇员的问答交流</span><br><span class="line">4）范围勘定</span><br><span class="line">I.确定项目起止时间</span><br><span class="line">II.项目授权信件</span><br><span class="line">III.进入目标规划环节</span><br><span class="line">5）确定IP和域名范围</span><br><span class="line">I.验证范围</span><br><span class="line">6）处理第三方资源</span><br><span class="line">I.云服务</span><br><span class="line">II.ISP（Internet Service Provider,互联网服务提供商）</span><br><span class="line">III.网站宿主</span><br><span class="line">IV.MSSP（Managed Security Service Provider,安全托管服务提供商）</span><br><span class="line">V.服务器所在国家</span><br><span class="line">7）定义可接受的社会工程学方法</span><br><span class="line">8）拒绝服务测试</span><br><span class="line">9）确定支付细节</span><br><span class="line">10）Delphi Scoping?（Delphi范围）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-目标规划"><a href="#2-目标规划" class="headerlink" title="2.目标规划"></a>2.目标规划</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1）确定目标</span><br><span class="line">I.首要目标</span><br><span class="line">II.额外目标</span><br><span class="line">2）业务分析</span><br><span class="line">I.定义目标企业的安全成熟度</span><br><span class="line">3）需求分析</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-测试术语和定义"><a href="#3-测试术语和定义" class="headerlink" title="3.测试术语和定义"></a>3.测试术语和定义</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1）渗透测试术语词汇表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-建立通讯渠道"><a href="#4-建立通讯渠道" class="headerlink" title="4.建立通讯渠道"></a>4.建立通讯渠道</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1）紧急联络方式</span><br><span class="line">2）应急响应流程</span><br><span class="line">3）进展报告周期</span><br><span class="line">4）确定一个接口联络人</span><br><span class="line">5）PGP或其他加密方式</span><br><span class="line">6）取得与外部第三方的联络方式（宿主...）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-交互确定规则"><a hre